snippet.title: C-Smash VRS New Dimension - Date Announcement Trailer | PS5 & PS VR2 Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-gb/games/c-smash-vrs/

Built on top of its PS VR2 predecessor, C-Smash VRS New Dimension comes to PlayStation 5 as a 3rd person futuristic sports action title, with tons of new gameplay mechanics, animations and visual upgrades, as well as revolutionary hybrid online play between PS5 and PS VR2 players.

#ps5 #ps5games #psvr2 #psvr2games
